				<p textAlign="center" fontFamily="MiSans" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">绝境 - N6<br/><span fontSize="24" color="#99ffff">Lv.110</span></p>
			</content>
			<filters>
				<DropShadowFilter angle="40" color="#99e5ff" distance="0" alpha="0.75" quality="2" blurX="25" blurY="25"/>
			</filters>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1180" y="729" fontFamily="MiSans" fontSize="13" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="bold" color="#b8b8b8" width="67" height="18" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.6">
			<content>
				<p textAlign="center" fontFamily="MiSans" fontSize="13" fontWeight="bold" color="#b8b8b8">× 9.3</p>
			</content>
			<filters>
				<DropShadowFilter angle="40" color="#99ccff" distance="16" alpha="0.75" quality="2" blurX="25" blurY="25"/>
			</filters>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="66" y="826" width="494" height="39" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">施放爆发时，<span color="#ffdfbf">消耗5%生命值</span><span>；爆发的第一段伤害命中时，</span><span color="#ffebbf">恢复5%生命值</span><span>；当生命值</span><span color="#ffebbf">低于20%</span><span>时，施放爆发改为</span><span color="#ffebbf">消耗10%当前生命值</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="66" y="538" width="507" height="116" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">施放爆发时，役人自身会立即获得白盾，厚度为<span color="#ffbfbf">22.5%生命值</span><span>，期间抗打断为0.01；击破白盾后役人将</span><span color="#ffdfbf">失去等量生命值</span><span>。<br/>白盾存在期间，役人将</span><span color="#ffbfbf">持续</span><span>向全队角色</span><span color="#ffbfbf">施加生命之契</span><span>，先施加</span><span color="#ffbfbf">500%</span><span>攻击力的生命之契，之后每0.5s施加</span><span color="#ffbfbf">75%</span><span>攻击力的生契。<br/>对于</span><span color="#ffbfbf">N5</span><span>和</span><span color="#ffacff">N6</span><span>难度，役人首次施加</span><span color="#ffdfbf">27100</span><span>/</span><span color="#ffdfbf">29028</span><span>点生命之契，后续每0.5秒施加</span><span color="#ffdfbf">4065</span><span>/</span><span color="#ffdfbf">4354</span><span>点生命之契。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="66" y="922" width="507" height="39" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">爆发的追加攻击对附有生命之契的目标造成的伤害提升<span color="#ffbfbf">150%</span><span>。被施加生命之契的目标，在遭受每段追加「猎杀」时都会累积生命之契。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<Rect x="576" y="32" width="768" height="768" alpha="1" d:userLabel="固定矩形" visible="false" blendMode="normal" radiusX="0" radiusY="0">
			<fill>
				<SolidColor color="#ffffff"/>
			</fill>
		</Rect>
		<RichText x="1199" y="934" fontFamily="MiSans" fontSize="16" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="bold" color="#ff4c4c" width="58" height="22" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.30196078431372547">
			<content>
				<p textAlign="center" fontFamily="MiSans" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ff4c4c">——</p>
			</content>
			<filters>
				<DropShadowFilter angle="40" color="#000000" distance="16" alpha="0.75" quality="2" blurX="25" blurY="25"/>
			</filters>
		</RichText>
