		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/迅悍之役-历经百战的霜役人%B7涉血芒锋.assets/Image_15.png')" x="1006" y="847" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="67" y="62" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#2686a2" width="207" height="28" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" color="#2686a2">制图@Csxylic米游社</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/迅悍之役-历经百战的霜役人%B7涉血芒锋.assets/Image_16.png')" x="1520" y="233">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="1538" y="320" width="433" height="151" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="18" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">霜役人瞄准目标，<span color="#ffebbf">消耗5%生命值</span><span>，2s后闪现发动攻击，对目标敌人造成</span><span color="#99ffff">40%</span><span>伤害并施加生命之契，随后发动追加「猎杀」攻击：<br/>闪现并发射一枚寒冰箭，造成</span><span color="#99ffff">50%</span><span>伤害并施加生命之契，随后冲刺下落，造成</span><span color="#99ffff">100%</span><span>伤害。<br/>被施加生命之契的目标，在遭受每段追加「猎杀」时都会累积生命之契。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/迅悍之役-历经百战的霜役人%B7涉血芒锋.assets/Image_17.png')" x="1396" y="267" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/迅悍之役-历经百战的霜役人%B7涉血芒锋.assets/Image_18.png')" x="1376" y="246" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="66" y="704" width="497" height="58" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">役人的爆发的每段伤害都会施加<span color="#ffbfbf">16%</span><span>攻击力的生命之契，且在该生命之契的影响下，被命中的角色将每秒流失</span><span color="#ffdfbf">(0.4%HP+72)</span><span>的生命值(后台止于5%)，持续10min，或清除生命之契后解除。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="650" y="931" fontFamily="MiSans" fontSize="16" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffebbf" width="128" height="22" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.6">
